WEBVTT

00:01.288 --> 00:02.990
♪ Search me ♪

00:02.991 --> 00:06.893
♪ Oh, Lord ♪

00:09.096 --> 00:11.065
♪ Search me ♪

00:11.066 --> 00:15.668
♪ Oh, Lord ♪

00:16.737 --> 00:18.539
♪ Shine your light ♪

00:18.540 --> 00:23.276
♪ Upon my heart, God ♪

00:24.545 --> 00:27.081
♪ Search our wickedness ♪

00:27.082 --> 00:31.351
♪ 'Til there is gone ♪

00:32.319 --> 00:34.321
♪ Search me ♪

00:34.322 --> 00:37.892
♪ Oh, Lord ♪

00:37.893 --> 00:40.628
♪

00:40.629 --> 00:43.763
- (WOMAN): Yes, yes, yes!
- (CHEERING)

00:46.067 --> 00:47.601
(MAN): She has a gift. Thank you!

00:47.602 --> 00:49.403
- (WOMAN): Girl!
- That was amazing.

00:49.404 --> 00:51.005
You should really sing more often.

00:51.006 --> 00:52.773
I'd love to, but I can't
let it get in the way

00:52.774 --> 00:55.342
- of my day job.
- OK, enough of the chit-chat.

00:55.343 --> 00:56.510
- Come now.
- Mama, the guests just

00:56.511 --> 00:58.679
got here, and Mr. Garvey
hasn't even arrived yet.

00:58.680 --> 01:01.482
Your generation is so lackadaisical.

01:01.483 --> 01:04.852
The Coloured Girls Orphanage is
depending on these donations.

01:04.852 --> 01:06.253
We can't skylark!

01:06.254 --> 01:09.356
Everything you organize turns
out perfectly, Mrs. Clarke.

01:09.357 --> 01:12.026
Oh. Well, that's because I
don't leave anything to chance.

01:12.027 --> 01:14.595
I even got some of
the orphan girls to come out.

01:14.596 --> 01:17.698
Nothing tugs at the heart
...or the purse strings...

01:17.699 --> 01:19.900
like children in need.

01:19.901 --> 01:23.137
- Hi, Trudy!
- Hi, Ismay!

01:23.138 --> 01:25.306
Oh, you've grown so much!

01:25.307 --> 01:27.308
I want to be just like you
when I grow up.

01:27.309 --> 01:29.210
- A singer?
- No, a detector!

01:29.211 --> 01:30.945
Oh!

01:30.946 --> 01:34.115
You mean a detective.
Well, in order to be that,

01:34.116 --> 01:36.117
you gotta do very well in school.

01:36.118 --> 01:38.419
Hey, you know what? This...

01:38.420 --> 01:41.822
would look really nice
with your dress.

01:41.823 --> 01:43.957
Thanks, Trudy!
I'm gonna wear it every day.

01:45.401 --> 01:46.792
Come on, let's get a
picture of you girls.

01:46.793 --> 01:47.932
Yes.

01:48.662 --> 01:50.498
- (CAMERA CLICKING)
- OK.

01:50.499 --> 01:52.500
Leave some film for Mr. Garvey.

01:52.501 --> 01:54.835
Just one... one more
to remember this day.

01:54.836 --> 01:56.537
Back to work young lady.

01:56.538 --> 01:59.039
Give them an inch, they take a yard.

01:59.040 --> 02:00.307
She's smitten with you.

02:00.308 --> 02:03.043
- She's sweet.
- Does no one want to do

02:03.044 --> 02:04.545
any work around here today?

02:04.546 --> 02:06.546
The money's not going
to collect itself!

02:07.448 --> 02:08.883
- Go!
- (TRUDY): OK, OK.

02:08.883 --> 02:10.518
I told you, Wesley, no.

02:10.519 --> 02:12.353
- Think this through.
- It's not your decision.

02:12.354 --> 02:13.988
Lionel, please don't do

02:13.989 --> 02:16.690
- anything rash...
- Stay out of it!

02:16.691 --> 02:18.626
Wesley. It's time.

02:18.627 --> 02:20.361
Lionel, I could use your help.

02:20.362 --> 02:22.028
Sure thing, Cora.

02:29.103 --> 02:30.771
Good afternoon, friends.

02:30.772 --> 02:34.074
I'm Wesley Hampton,
President of the Toronto chapter

02:34.075 --> 02:36.710
of the U.N.I.A., and I welcome you all

02:36.711 --> 02:38.412
in the spirit of unity.

02:38.413 --> 02:42.183
Today, we are raising funds for
the Coloured Girls Orphanage.

02:42.184 --> 02:44.018
But it's not just
a roof over their heads

02:44.019 --> 02:46.086
and food in their mouths
that we're giving them.

02:46.087 --> 02:47.788
With your support,

02:47.789 --> 02:49.857
we will create a library

02:49.858 --> 02:51.659
so that a new generation of girls

02:51.660 --> 02:54.661
will grow into educated young women.

02:56.564 --> 02:58.264
(OVERLAPPING ACCLAMATIONS)

02:59.934 --> 03:02.102
Now, it is my honour

03:02.103 --> 03:04.104
to bring to the stage

03:04.105 --> 03:07.141
the founder of the United Negro
Improvement Association,

03:07.142 --> 03:09.076
the honourable

03:09.077 --> 03:12.613
Marcus... Mosiah... Garvey!

03:12.614 --> 03:14.647
(CHEERING)

03:16.000 --> 03:22.074
